C4E.description:
The native token of Chain4Energy

C4E is a DePIN L1 Blockchain platform, designed to support a variety of innovative energy and e-mobility applications by creating a decentralized and democratized community-powered ecosystem.

edgeSOL(dot)pica.description: A representative token for staked SOL, derived through the process of liquid staking SOL using the Edgevana protocol.

LST(dot)pica.description: A representative token for staked SOL, derived through the process of liquid staking SOL using the MarginFi protocol.

jitoSOL(dot)pica.description: A representative token for staked SOL, derived through the process of liquid staking SOL using Jito.

wSOL(dot)pica.description: SOL is the native cryptocurrency of the Solana blockchain.

allUSDT.description:
An alloy of USDT asset variants on Osmosis.

Multiple Tether USD variants on Osmosis comprise the liquidity backing of a tokenized transmuter pool to create an alloy of USDT.
